{
  "stem": "26022.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, by then, my father had his own factory, an incandescent lamp factory.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They made all kinds of shapes and colors.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he had some very, very big contracts, like the theaters, some of the theaters in Vienna.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We'll come back to the theater later.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Some of the theaters in Vienna, he had a contract with that whatever lights and bulbs and spotlights and whatever a theater needs, we'll supply for a fixed amount per year, whatever term the contract ran.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And of course sometimes we got passes.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And so it a very sizable-- I mean, it wasn't the General Electric or anything, but it was a pretty important part of our lives, at least, but also of the Austrian economy.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We want to say that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And so he came back to his office on the next trolley, I suppose.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was too far to walk.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And this went on-- Hitler came in March.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "This went on for a few weeks, and these were some harrowing weeks because so many people who owed had left and those who hadn't left didn't pay because it was a Jewish firm.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we had-- of course, we had representatives who acquired business.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And one of them, who was always very, very courteous and a very nice, gentlemen, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] decided that as long as my father couldn't keep the place, why didn't he take over?",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "At least we're on friendly terms, and he's not going to hurt anybody.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And why should he always have to use his shoe leather to acquire customers if you could sit at the office and just pick up the phone?",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's what he thought an owner or a boss does.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
